### Order Processing API - HTTP Client Requests
### Base URL: http://localhost:5000
### Start the application with: dotnet run --project OrderProcessingWithDi

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000

### ============================================================================
### DI Endpoints
### ============================================================================

### POST /orders - Create Order
POST {{baseUrl}}/orders?productId=A1&quantity=6&unitPrice=10

### GET /orders - Get All Orders
GET {{baseUrl}}/orders

### GET /di-demo - Demonstrate Service Lifetimes
GET {{baseUrl}}/di-demo

### GET /factory-demo - Demonstrate Factory Pattern
GET {{baseUrl}}/factory-demo?price=10&quantity=6&serviceType=standard

### GET /factory-demo - Simple Service
GET {{baseUrl}}/factory-demo?price=10&quantity=6&serviceType=simple

### ============================================================================
### Routing Endpoints
### ============================================================================

### GET /api/v1/orders - Get All Orders (v1)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/orders

### GET /api/v1/orders/{orderId} - Get Order by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/orders/0

### GET /api/v1/orders/product/{productId} - Get Orders by Product ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/orders/product/A1

### GET /api/v1/orders/range/{minTotal}/{maxTotal} - Get Orders by Total Range
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/orders/range/50/100

### GET /api/v1/orders/search - Search Orders (all parameters optional)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/orders/search?productId=A1&minTotal=50&maxTotal=100&limit=10

### GET /api/v1/orders/search - Search Orders (minimal parameters)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/orders/search

### GET /api/v1/orders/recent/{days} - Get Recent Orders (range 1-30)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/orders/recent/7

### GET /api/v1/orders/stats - Get Order Statistics
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/orders/stats

### ============================================================================
### Configuration Endpoints
### ============================================================================

### GET /config/pricing - Get Pricing Configuration
GET {{baseUrl}}/config/pricing

### GET /config/order-processing - Get Order Processing Configuration
GET {{baseUrl}}/config/order-processing

### GET /config/application - Get Application Configuration
GET {{baseUrl}}/config/application

### GET /config/all - Get All Configuration
GET {{baseUrl}}/config/all

### GET /config/raw - Get Raw Configuration (using IConfiguration)
GET {{baseUrl}}/config/raw

### ============================================================================
### Error Handling Examples
### ============================================================================

### GET /api/v1/orders/{orderId} - Order Not Found (404)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/orders/99999

### POST /orders - Invalid Order (400 Bad Request)
POST {{baseUrl}}/orders?productId=&quantity=5&unitPrice=10

### POST /orders - Zero Quantity (400 Bad Request)
POST {{baseUrl}}/orders?productId=A1&quantity=0&unitPrice=10

### POST /orders - Negative Price (400 Bad Request)
POST {{baseUrl}}/orders?productId=A1&quantity=5&unitPrice=-10
